The '''Blockade Runners Derby''' was a competition held by [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] in the comet cloud around [[Ord Mantell/Legends|Ord Mantell]]. It was held annually since [[69 BBY/Legends|69 BBY]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] won three times and in [[24 ABY/Legends|24 ABY]], during its 93rd anniversary, held the title of [[Grand Marshal of the Blockade Runners Derby|Grand Marshal]]. The same year, [[Zekk]] won the derby in his ship, the ''[[Lightning Rod]]''. There were other participants that complained when it was revealed that the winner was [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]], however Zekk had only used his innate [[The Force/Legends|Force]] abilities alone, while the other competitors had modified ships for the derby.

